e holds a masters in finance accounting and corporate law from decf in paris and a bachelors in economics from paris x nanterre university he has lived in luxembourg paris brussels and new york throughout his career and now resides in london related stories coty inc to webcast second quarter fiscal  financial results on february   coty inc to webcast first quarter fiscal  financial results on november   as the leader of the finance function my mission is to make sure that i provide the right tools and equipment to everybody so we can grow patrice de talhouët archives  cdr – chain drug review × search in site to search in site type your keyword and hit enter close patrice de talhouët revlon buys cutex businesses from coty june   by chain drug review coty cutex gianni pieraccioni nail care patrice de talhouët revlon supplier news new york — revlon inc has acquired coty inc’s international businesses for nail care brand cutex financial terms of the deal weren’t disclosed revlon said monday that with the transaction it has completed the global consolidation of the cutex brand’s worldwide operations under revlon management the businesses acquired operate mainly in australia and the united search videos  slideshows videos slideshows usmade hello products highlighted by walmart nacds offers input to us drug abuse commission walgreens rite aid deal is downsized how walgreens’ red nose day helps kids gmdc spotlights gm product showcase winners london drugs launches ldexpress format rite aid reopens harrisburg market street store walgreens florida hospital open  instore clinics latest from the cdr blog its a milestone for publix th pharmacypostscript on walgreensrite aid merger sagaaam rems abuse trips up new genericspharmacy far from slam dunk for amazonamazon eyeing pharmacy space news archives  categories news archives  categories select category business   cdr blog   featured articles   issues               issue          issue          issue          issue          issue